Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku harus memastikan\Nserangan berikutnya kena!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Serangan terakhirnya...{\i0}
