Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rasa sakit saat tubuhnya hancur,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}kesulitan bernapas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dalam kondisi itu, manusia normal\Nakan fokus mempertahankan nyawanya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Manusia normal, ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak masalah. Akan kuhancurkan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau, negara ini,\Ndan semuanya yang menghalangi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan ini, aku bisa melakukan transfer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan ini, aku akan bunuh dia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pengguna Keenam. Tabir Asap!{\i0}
