Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}kau terpaksa harus bertahan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia koyak tanah\Nuntuk hentikan penyebaran Pembusukan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kapan dia memasang rantai besar itu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tadi, saat dia terpental,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dia tancapkan Rantai Hitam ke bawah tanah\Nuntuk mengoyak sebagian tanah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bersiap untuk tahap selanjutnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Metode ini...{\i0}
