Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jadi, aku lempar jubah\Nyang berlumuran darahku ke Shigaraki.{\i0}
